than the shit I took this morning.

13:13.876 --> 13:14.793
Sit.

13:17.296 --> 13:20.132
I'll be honest with you,
I watch your films

13:20.216 --> 13:21.967
and I see the same male apery

13:22.051 --> 13:24.887
that has spread like a cancer
through this industry,

13:24.970 --> 13:28.015
and I'm sure this meeting
is a waste of my time.

13:29.850 --> 13:30.893
But...

13:31.894 --> 13:38.692
I watched your speech, and I felt,
"Maybe, maybe, this is my Jordi."

13:41.278 --> 13:44.031
So, do you, uh... do you know the scene?

13:44.114 --> 13:46.283
Yes, yes. I know-- I know the lines.

13:46.367 --> 13:49.578
Okay, good. Then break my heart.

14:01.090 --> 14:02.675
Can I have a moment, sir?

14:03.259 --> 14:04.134
Yeah.

14:06.637 --> 14:08.764
No, no, no. Not now. Not now.

14:09.557 --> 14:11.600
[sighs] Puh! Puh!

14:12.726 --> 14:14.812
[trilling]

14:17.273 --> 14:20.109
