14:43.215 --> 14:44.884
Do you want me to stay?

14:48.554 --> 14:50.347
Yes. Yes.

14:50.848 --> 14:52.057
Why?

14:52.141 --> 14:55.394
I've always been alone.

14:55.477 --> 14:57.938
When I was just a little kid,

14:58.022 --> 15:01.442
I was left alone and I'm afraid...

15:02.902 --> 15:04.403
I will always be alone.

15:04.486 --> 15:06.238
No. No.

15:06.322 --> 15:08.449
Uh... fake. Bullshit.

15:08.532 --> 15:09.408
I'm sorry.

15:09.491 --> 15:11.619
