15:14.163 --> 15:15.205
Fuck apologies.

15:15.831 --> 15:18.709
-Start again. I want truth.
-Okay.

15:22.546 --> 15:23.380
The truth.

15:24.882 --> 15:26.300
The truth is...

15:27.217 --> 15:29.219
