15:33.098 --> 15:33.974
The truth is...

15:34.850 --> 15:36.769
I make the best Sidecars in the world.

16:17.601 --> 16:18.519
Perfect.

16:32.282 --> 16:33.826
Do you want me to stay?

16:39.707 --> 16:40.708
No.

16:42.376 --> 16:43.419
Why?

16:45.546 --> 16:47.297
I've always been alone.

16:49.842 --> 16:51.510
Even as a child.

16:55.139 --> 16:57.725
