and took every golden inch up my ass.

19:19.116 --> 19:21.368
Marc! Sweetie.

19:21.451 --> 19:23.453
Come here, I want you to meet our Jordi.

19:23.537 --> 19:26.290
This is Marc Jacobs, he's our designer.
And Charlie.

19:26.373 --> 19:28.542
-Hi. Kit told us all about you.
-Hi.

19:29.126 --> 19:30.961
-We saw your speech.
-It was beautiful.

19:31.044 --> 19:32.337
Thank you. Thank you.

19:32.421 --> 19:34.173
I love that you brought him
up there with you.

19:34.756 --> 19:36.925
-My partner, Hernando.
-Hi.

19:37.009 --> 19:38.218
-Hello.
-That kiss...

19:38.302 --> 19:40.804
-So hot.
-Yeah. So romantic.

19:40.888 --> 19:43.473
I mean, gay men are supposed
to only be about their cocks.

19:43.557 --> 19:47.352
