19:57.321 --> 20:02.367
Okay. Well, first of all,
Jordi would never wear this.

20:02.451 --> 20:04.119
Not this.

20:06.914 --> 20:07.831
No.

20:07.915 --> 20:09.875
Not the shoes. Those go.

20:12.127 --> 20:13.921
Not these pants.

20:15.339 --> 20:16.798
I mean...

20:20.844 --> 20:22.596
Don't worry. Don't worry.

20:23.388 --> 20:25.766
I've always said
that if all the world's a stage,

20:25.849 --> 20:28.518
