21:57.441 --> 21:59.985
[indistinct chatter]

22:11.038 --> 22:12.914
[cheering]

22:21.548 --> 22:26.970
Oh-ho! [chuckles] Whoo!
Hey, man, look at you.

22:27.054 --> 22:29.306
[chanting] Van Damn! Van Damn!

22:32.851 --> 22:33.685
Mom?

22:35.437 --> 22:36.521
Oh, my son.

22:41.818 --> 22:43.361
If your father could see you now.

22:47.449 --> 22:49.534
He would be so proud.

22:56.625 --> 22:57.626
We should go.

22:57.709 --> 23:00.212
He's right. If we're late,
they'll think we're afraid, no?

23:00.295 --> 23:02.756
[all shouting, cheering]

23:05.967 --> 23:09.179
[chanting] Van Damn! Van Damn!

23:09.262 --> 23:11.807
-We can avoid the traffic on Nyong by--
-Leave it to us.

23:11.890 --> 23:14.518
You're not a bus driver anymore.
We'll get you there.

23:17.229 --> 23:19.731
[chanting continues]

23:39.793 --> 23:43.880
Blake? Blake Huntington? You come here.

23:46.341 --> 23:48.343
-Oh, my gosh. That's Blake Huntington.
-Oh, my God!

23:48.426 --> 23:49.511
That's Blake Huntington.

23:49.594 --> 23:53.640
Please, guys. Guys, please.
Please, please. Come on. Act normal.

23:54.099 --> 23:57.227
