to introduce you.

23:57.310 --> 23:58.895
This is our Jordi Gallo.

23:59.437 --> 24:02.482
It is a pleasure to meet you, Blake.
It's a pleasure. It's an honor.

24:02.566 --> 24:04.025
So it went well.

24:04.109 --> 24:05.402
Tears.

24:06.153 --> 24:07.612
Copious tears.

24:09.406 --> 24:16.246
And Jordi, this is the man that you are
willing to die for: Pablo de la Cruz.

24:16.329 --> 24:17.747
-He's Pablo?
-He's Pablo?

24:18.540 --> 24:19.457
I am.

24:19.541 --> 24:21.042
The deal was inked yesterday.

24:21.126 --> 24:22.586
We're...

24:24.671 --> 24:26.590
