back home.

24:48.862 --> 24:51.198
Thank you. Thank you, that's very kind.

24:51.281 --> 24:53.700
Hernando, Dani, please,
don't embarrass the man.

24:54.534 --> 24:55.702
And you are?

24:56.203 --> 24:57.913
