and the dark of night."

25:42.123 --> 25:43.166
The Lady and the Dog.

25:43.250 --> 25:44.334
It is.

25:45.252 --> 25:47.128
Iberian Dreams reminds me of Chekhov.

25:47.212 --> 25:48.630
It does.

25:48.713 --> 25:50.799
-[laughs]
-Please, stop. Please, stop it.

25:50.882 --> 25:53.885
