with your fucking literary bullshit.

25:53.969 --> 25:56.930
Just answer one question honestly.

25:57.514 --> 25:58.723
Do you want to fuck him?

26:00.183 --> 26:01.601
As Pablo?

26:03.311 --> 26:04.604
Absolutely.

26:07.107 --> 26:08.066
Thank you.

26:10.694 --> 26:13.238
[cheering]

26:35.343 --> 26:36.344
